  "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds the complete **Dealix Startup Company OS (V5)** as a named, verifiable, **additive and non-destructive** layer over the existing engines — spanning company strategy, product, engineering, website, commercial GTM, sales, marketing, media/social, ads planning, a 400+ daily founder-review draft factory, CRM/RevOps, delivery, support, finance, legal/compliance, security/trust, analytics, AI evals, people, partnerships, investor readiness, operations, go-live, and final launch control.\n\n> **Non-negotiable rule, enforced by tests:** AI drafts, analyzes, scores, ranks, recommends, and prepares. The founder reviews, approves, sells, sends manually, and signs off. **The system never sends externally.**\n\n## Includes\n- Company OS · Product OS · Engineering OS · Website Launch OS · Commercial Launch OS (+5 vertical playbooks) · Sales OS · Marketing OS · Media/Social OS · Ads OS\n- 400+ review-only **Draft Factory** + Founder Review Queue · CRM/RevOps OS · Delivery OS · Support OS\n- Finance OS · Legal/Compliance OS · Security/Trust OS · Analytics OS · AI Evals OS\n- People OS · Partnerships OS · Investor OS · Operations OS · Go-Live OS · **Launch Control Tower**\n- 5 GitHub Actions · verification scripts · 18 V5 test files · evidence reports\n- 18 static Next.js launch pages · README Startup OS section · stale `VoXc2 → Dealix-sa` fix\n\n## Safety\n- No external sending. No SMTP / WhatsApp / LinkedIn automation. No scraping. No form auto-submit. No live paid ads. No secrets.\n- Every draft carries forced flags: `send_allowed=false`, `external_send_blocked=true`, `requires_founder_approval=true`, `no_auto_send=true`.\n- All GitHub Actions are `permissions: contents: read`, artifact-only, no secrets, no daily output commits.\n\n## Tests Run (real results)\n| Gate | Result |\n|------|--------|\n| `python scripts/startup_os_verify.py` | **PASS — 94/94, 0 critical failures** |\n| `python scripts/final_launch_control_verify.py` | **GO** (15/15 critical steps PASS) |\n| V5 pytest suite (18 files) | **30 passed** |\n| `apps/web` `npm run typecheck && npm run build` | **PASS** (20 V5 routes prerendered static) |\n| `make env-check` | **PASS** |\n| `final_secret_and_risk_scan.py` (V5 surface) | **PASS** (337 files, 0 findings) |\n| `make security-smoke` (whole repo) | **FAIL — pre-existing**, not V5 (see below) |\n\n**Pre-existing `security-smoke` failures** flag sample/placeholder secrets in existing fixtures/docs only (`tests/test_billing_moyasar_safety.py`, `tests/test_v5_layers_pt4.py`, `tests/test_finance_os_no_live_charge_invariant.py`, `tests/test_dealix_invoice_cli.py`, `docs/ops/GO_LIVE_CHECKLIST_AR.md`, `docs/launch/DEALIX_LAUNCH_NOW_BUNDLE.md`). No V5 file is flagged; recommend a separate security PR to scrub/allowlist these.\n\n> Note: V5 tests are intentionally self-contained and run independently of the full app stack via `--noconftest`. The broader repo suite requires the complete app dependencies.\n\n## Final Go/No-Go\n**GO:** public website launch, commercial positioning, 400+ review-only drafts, founder manual review, media/social planning + manual posting, paid diagnostics, discovery, proposals, pilot planning, analytics schema, delivery/support prep, finance/legal templates (pending legal review), investor/partnership/hiring readiness.\n\n**NO-GO (forbidden):** automated email/WhatsApp/LinkedIn sending, form auto-submit, bulk sending, live paid ads without tracking/compliance, sensitive data before agreement, external sends from Actions, claims not backed by evidence.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01DfFAFESF824pHgL6MpCD79\n\n---\n_Generated by [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code/session_01DfFAFESF824pHgL6MpCD79)_",
